data.description: Charming brick home features open floor plan with spacious great room, handsome fireplace & open dining room. You will love the large covered back patio & covered 2 car carport. Primary suite is also spacious and features 2 walk in closets, and a new shower in the main bath. Kitchen features room for a breakfast table, with nice views of the backyard area and great cabinet storage. Excellent location just minutes to all East Montgomery offers, and easy access to the Interstate & bypass. Make your appointment today!
